Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"White Room" "Large Window" "Mayu"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:28.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ta... Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:18.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:02:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, you were okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,But... why is Tama-{\i1}chan {\i0}there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,...why is Urith a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't she supposed to fulfill your wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.99,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,to a certain extent, already fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why battle now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Even about Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That's just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Such tasteless play...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's scary! She'll be hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle staaart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Please go easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you please not speak to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama is my LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish Crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Yaaargh! So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?! Is it happening?!\NFinally happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,My rival appears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,All righty! This is getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't anything to be happy about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Chorizo In The Fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Say the name of the move properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Cloth Crash Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so one-sided...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Chiyori's going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop... Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need to listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,She threw you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No! Ru was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Get Bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It... It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems Tama is fine without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at how vividly she's enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing changed about her\Never since she was your LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...the only one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama... You're not having fun, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--Eldora, Grow! And now, Kozame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama was a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I went bye-bye from Ru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Baroque Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sh... Shiira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, c'mon, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not something you say\Nwhen they're prepped, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle was so fun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It was fun doing it with Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not fun because I'm with Urith...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Salvage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama isn't... having fun battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was battling Iona-{\i1}san{\i0},\NI didn't think I could return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Yuzuki, Hitoe, and all the other\Ngirls who turned into LRIGs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If everyone could be saved,\NI thought that would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But... that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I was lonely without you, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama was... lonely too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because I didn't talk\Nabout my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because I made you worried, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I should have talked more to you, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Talked so that you would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Because Tama, you're my...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,And... what the heck are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Because! Tama and Ru were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Them now battling as enemies is so cliché!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,So cliché!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm gonna cry... I love clichés!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I can get my satisfaction just with clichés!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:58.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I really don't think this is the time\Nto be saying things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,With the next attack, we're going to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Such a horrible girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Doing it with me, and yet\Nthinking of someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What a turn-off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me back Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want her back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...battle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, don't battle! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You too... Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,See you again, scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I know Tama is okay now,\Nand that she feels the same way as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry I made both of you\Nworried, Hitoe, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What a nice turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,A torn friendship and a rival appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool, and cool! So super!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,We told her at length not to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you care about what's\Ngoing to happen to Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, now. I talked about\Nit in depth too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I talked about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Lookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Chorizo De Ibéricoña The Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Chorizo? As in the sausage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Boop-boop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Chiyori's name when I become an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You see? She just became even more excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But... you lost to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And you lost to Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So you lost twice already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,But, but, I already won three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish could come true\Nat any moment, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose again,\Nyour wish is going to be reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The heroine in the novel loses twice too,\Nbut ends up beating her rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And then before she knows it,\Nshe's at White Garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,White... Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup! A hyper-dimensional white void!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,White?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...that white room I was at\Nwhen I became an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Does a room appear in that novel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...?! I gave you a copy of the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, um... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori-{\i1}san{\i0}? Do you mind\Nletting us read that novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wings of Lament Mark{\i0}\N{\i1}the Dreams of the Ruined Land{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Futase Fumio"\NFutase Fumio...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,In a future not far from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,mysterious beings called "LRIG"\Nappear throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIGs connect themselves to\Nyoung girls with special powers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and are able to make their wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,In order for the wish to come true,\Nthey need to defeat other LRIGs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,and gather the WIXOSS factors from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A young girl meets an LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,and is drawn into the battle for wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This young girl, who won her battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,ends up in the time labyrinth, White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,White Garden? This is the\Nwhite windowed room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The word "Selector" doesn't appear,\Nbut this all sounds so similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's written to sound cool, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yessy! She finally appears!\NThe Dark Lord of Atonement, Cocoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,The ruler of White Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The almighty being that holds\Ndominion over all the WIXOSS battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she like, a last boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it ends here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The suspense! Hurry with the next volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Cocoon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that English for "{\i1}mayu{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,White room... Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.99,Main,,0,0,0,,She must know something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Futase Fumio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It says here that she originally\Nannounced her novel over the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What she wrote as a pastime caught\Nthe attention of a person working at a publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The first book was published, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...she wrote the second book,\Nbut the series stopped there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Could she be a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But... why would she glamorize it in her works?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If she knows about the white room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,she should know what would happen\Nif someone continued battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We could find out a lot of things if we ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A lot, as in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,About Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,...and about Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, you said something about\Nhow Tama could be a "special girl," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Not all Eternal Girls are normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Among them may be a special girl\Nwho holds mysterious powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, not sure, but I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,...there's a way to make the LRIGs return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what Tama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, come to think of it, where's Chiyori-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.95,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yaaargh!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,There. Six wins in a row for Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Urrh... You're too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't try harder,\Nyou're not going to get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Could you be the Sorcerer of Blood?!\NThe Danger Zone of WIXOSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Queen of Innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if you win, Chiyori-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you two join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ruko"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ruko"\NAh! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's the novel's website.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Futase Fumio" "Official Website"\NIt's still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.95,Main,,0,0,0,,"Futase Fumio-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse us for our sudden e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We read your novel, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be very upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We're Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei, are you aware of Selectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If so, please allow us\Nan opportunity to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Kominato Ruko. Uemura Hitoe."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that sound okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"Send"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,See ya laters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll contact you when we get a reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Be sure to come with us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Will we... get a reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Like how Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}and Urith-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nbecame Selectors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no coincidence that Tama\Nbecame Urith's LRIG, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:17:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... came to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's her doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But, why? Why would she do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?! It just makes everyone confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you girls battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,All the while confused\Nby incomprehensible rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're all just being played by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Selectors and LRIGs...\Nare all just dolls to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,All she's doing is playing with her dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Playing with dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,She's enjoying seeing\Nthe dolls battle each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,There was a lot that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:04.50,Main,,0,0,0,,but I'm happy you got to see Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama pairs up best next to you, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best so that Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}\Ncan come back to you, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,--Good night.\N--Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Those two are... unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, it's Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,How has Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She calmed down quite a bit,\Nall because of you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl... Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you help me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Truly disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Regarding Selectors"\N"Futase Fumio"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:17.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Futase Fumio-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what it said in the e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Nervous! Nervous! Super nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So sorry here! She's surprisingly timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Shuffle, shuffle, shuffle, shuffle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello... I sent an e-mail yesterday. Kominato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,"White Room" "Large Window" "Mayu"\NWhite room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"White Room" "Large Window" "Mayu"\NMayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Large window...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,White room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Large window...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,White room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hello...?\N--Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,--Are you... Futase Fumio-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?\N--Large room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:56.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... Futase Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:02.07,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Those Wild Delusions"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:15.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:43.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:05.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:12.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:17.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...don't you know more than\Nwhat's written in the novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can defeat me in battle,\NI'll tell you everything that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,How much do you think she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with that form?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Impatience Is an Awakening"\NThis Impatience Is an Awakening.
